<title>qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb .. qd tjlt fy ạlṣlyb
 qd rwạhạ ly ḥbyby .. sạʿẗ ạlṣmt ạlrhyb
 whw msḥwq ạlfw̉ạd .. whw mjrwḥ ạljbyn
 qd rwạhạ ly ḥbyby .. bạldm ạlgẖạly ạltẖmyn
 1- kạn bạlạ̉ms yjwl .. yṣnʿ ạlkẖyr ạlʿẓym
 wynạdy bạlḥyạẗ .. ysẖfy jrḥnạ ạlạ̉lym
 kạn ḥbh ʿjybaⁿạ .. ạ̹dẖ ạ̉ḥb ạlậtẖmyn
 dẖạ lạ̉nh yswʿ .. qd ạ̉ḥb kl ḥyn
 2- bynmạ ạlḥb yjwl .. kạn fkr ạlḥạqdyn
 kyf yqtlwạ yswʿ .. ạ̹dẖ ạ̉ḥb ạlmdẖnbyn
 ḥty̱ tnthy ạlrwạyẗ .. qṣẗ ạlḥb ạltẖmyn
 ḥty̱ tktb ạlnhạyẗ .. mạt byn ạlmjrmyn
 3- qd ạ̉hyn ạlḥb ẓlmaⁿạ .. qd ạ̉hyn bạlṣlyb
 mnṭq ạlnạs tlạsẖy̱ .. ạ̹dẖ bdạ ạlḥb ạlskyb
 ạ̹nh ḥb sybqy̱ .. ạ̉bd ạldhr ykwn
 lys ḥb mtẖl hdẖạ .. ṣạdqaⁿạ dwmaⁿạ ḥnwn
 4- ạ̉y ḥb qd tnạhy̱ .. mtẖl ḥbh ạlʿjyb
 ạ̉y ḥb mtẖl hdẖạ .. qd bdạ bʿd ạlṣlyb
 kl ḥb fy ạlwjwd .. nbʿh ḥb yswʿ
 kl ḥb fy kyạny .. rdh ḥb yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>